---
title: Chicken Thai Yellow Style Curry with Sweet Potato and Greens
description: Turmeric in combination with red chillies help make Thai Yellow different from the other colours of curry in Thai cuisine, resulting in a milder sauce. Here, our Chicken Thai Yellow Style Curry heroes the veg as well as the meat.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R43_W35_UK_V19728-7__Main_2low-fd9752f5.jpg
